sourcesContent: "use strict";exports.__esModule=true;exports.rewriteStacktrace=rewriteStacktrace;var filenameRE=/\(([^)]+\.js):(\d+):(\d+)\)$/;function rewriteStacktrace(e,distDir){if(!e||typeof e.stack!=='string'){return;}var lines=e.stack.split('\n');var result=lines.map(line=>{return rewriteTraceLine(line,distDir);});e.stack=result.join('\n');}function rewriteTraceLine(trace,distDir){var m=trace.match(filenameRE);if(m==null){return trace;}var filename=m[1];var filenameLink=filename.replace(distDir,'/_next/development').replace(/\\/g,'/');trace=trace.replace(filename,filenameLink);return trace;}
